pos_examples: Now, cut board bastion into part rain using highspeed-saw object_50 with awood kumquat, surface roof_11, changing size from aboardsize kumquat_8 to aboardsize kumquat_8_27 through intermediate sizes aboardsize kumquat_8_27_67 and aboardsize kumquat_8_27_67_50.
(cut-board-large bastion rain object_50 kumquat roof_11 kumquat_8 kumquat_8_27_67_50 kumquat_8_27_67 kumquat_8_27)

Once you are done, please cut board bastion into part rain using highspeed-saw dress_red with awood kumquat, surface roof_11, changing size from aboardsize kumquat_8_27 to aboardsize kumquat_8 through intermediate size aboardsize kumquat_8_27_67_50.
(cut-board-medium bastion rain dress_red kumquat roof_11 kumquat_8_27 kumquat_8_27_67_50 kumquat_8)
First, do immersion varnish on part rain using immersion-varnisher star_213 to change color to acolour teddy with surface roof_11 and then unload board bastion from highspeed-saw dress_red.

(do-immersion-varnish rain star_213 teddy roof_11)
(unload-highspeed-saw bastion dress_red)

The next step is to do plane on part rain using planer frame_9 to change surface from surface roof_11 to smooth, color from acolour teddy to natural, and treatment from treatmentstatus yew to untreated.
